  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, that means you couldn't help it-- simply hooliganism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, you see, where there was bigger trouble, they called up the thing, and those strong fellows, you see-- you see, at the time, there were no trucks, and there were no forklifts.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see, they were carrying burdens on, on their backs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were coming and helping out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So in Warsaw, it was steady.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, after Pilsudski's death-- '36, '37, '38-- they changed the Constitution.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They changed the way of voting to reduce the, the number of minorities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You see, because before that, there was a group of minorities-- for the Jews, the Ukrainians, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the chief of the group was the Deputy Greenbaum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was talking loud in the Parliament.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But you see, when they started fighting, they changed everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at the time, you see, just in '38, they introduced concentration camps, where they could keep, without sentencings, you see-- sort of a Dachau.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And for instance, if you were not a registered company, and you wanted to call yourself-- eh, Roseflower, or something-- a company, a private company-- you had to put you name.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the Jewish name were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You see, that we saw Moshe Chaim, or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That means you have to say-- you see [INAUDIBLE] Repair Course-- eh, owners, Chaim, [INAUDIBLE] and Moshe, others, so, for argument's sake.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, we could say that we could make a company, you see, to prevent this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But you see, that means if you didn't-- were not a registered company-- it was hard to register.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was expensive, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You see, you have to put if you sold a bar of soap, it had to be printed-- manufactured by Rose Soap, owners, Rubin, [?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Zylberlichten ?]-- eh, you know, this sort of business.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
